    through Purrfection!</h2>
  <!-- Most Recent Ads Posted -->

<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-orange-500 border-black col-span-12 bg-white shadow-md py-4 px-10 mt-4">Recently added pets:</h3>

  <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 shadow-md col-span-12 mx-auto md:col-start-2 md:col-end-6 my-4 max-w-sm">
